<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>HTML</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>HEAD</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>TITLE</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>The document title<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>TITLE</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
